5. Given three integers a, b and c. The task is to check if it is possible to make right angled triangle with sides of length a, b and c.
Platform : GeeksForGeeks
SOURCE CODE :class Solution {
    static String rightAngTri(long a, long b, long c) {
       long  max=Math.max(a,Math.max(b,c));
       if(max==a){
           return (b*b+c*c==a*a)?"Yes":"No";
       }
       else if (max==b){
           return (a*a+c*c==b*b)?"Yes":"No";
       }
       else {
           return (a*a+b*b==c*c)?"Yes":"No";
       }
    }
}
Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/right-angled-triangles4729/1
